  borderObjectName: TRUNGQUOC
  countryDescription: "\u0110\u01B0\u1EDDng bi\xEAn gi\u1EDBi \u0111\u1EA5t li\u1EC1n
    Vi\u1EC7t - Trung d\xE0i kho\u1EA3ng 1.281 km, b\u1EAFt \u0111\u1EA7u t\u1EEB
    ng\xE3 ba bi\xEAn gi\u1EDBi Vi\u1EC7t - L\xE0o - Trung (A Pa Ch\u1EA3i, \u0110i\u1EC7n
    Bi\xEAn) \u0111\u1EBFn \u0111i\u1EC3m k\u1EBFt th\xFAc t\u1EA1i c\u1EEDa s\xF4ng
    B\u1EAFc Lu\xE2n (M\xF3ng C\xE1i, Qu\u1EA3ng Ninh).\n\nSau c\xE1c \u0111\u1EE3t
    s\u1EAFp x\u1EBFp \u0111\u1ECBa gi\u1EDBi h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh, \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng
    bi\xEAn gi\u1EDBi n\xE0y hi\u1EC7n \u0111i qua 7 t\u1EC9nh bi\xEAn gi\u1EDBi
    ph\xEDa B\u1EAFc bao g\u1ED3m: \u0110i\u1EC7n Bi\xEAn, Lai Ch\xE2u, L\xE0o Cai,
    Tuy\xEAn , Cao B\u1EB1ng, L\u1EA1ng S\u01A1n v\xE0 Qu\u1EA3ng Ninh. \u0110\xE2y
    l\xE0 khu v\u1EF1c c\xF3 \u0111\u1ECBa h\xECnh n\xFAi cao, hi\u1EC3m tr\u1EDF
    nh\u01B0ng \u0111\xF3ng vai tr\xF2 l\xE0 c\u1EEDa ng\xF5 giao th\u01B0\u01A1ng
    kinh t\u1EBF \u0111\u1EB7c bi\u1EC7t quan tr\u1ECDng gi\u1EEFa Vi\u1EC7t Nam
    v\xE0 c\xE1c t\u1EC9nh ph\xEDa Nam Trung Qu\u1ED1c th\xF4ng qua h\u1EC7 th\u1ED1ng
    c\u1EEDa kh\u1EA9u qu\u1ED1c t\u1EBF s\u1EA7m u\u1EA5t."
